
### Step 4: Auto Posting
- **Tool:** Taskade AI / Make.com / Zapier  
- **Integration:** LinkedIn or Twitter API  
- **Automation:** Runs daily at 9 AM IST and posts content automatically.

---

## ⚙️ Tools Used
- **Taskade AI** – Workflow automation & AI summarization  
- **ChatGPT API** – Text generation & summarization  
- **Google News RSS** – News source  
- **LinkedIn API / Twitter API** – Auto posting  
- **GitHub** – Code & documentation storage  

